content: It wasn't free. She got paid a lot of money by a Brazilian bank and Rio's city hall. The show was horrible. As always she uses sex scenes as a blasphemy and etc.. All her career has been based on controversy. She's not a good singer... she's not a good human. She's greedy and unkind.
